    • Method Detail

      • get

        java.lang.String get(java.lang.String parameterName)
        Returns the value associated with the provided parameterName.

        The method must not return null when a provided parameterName exists in the FormDataMapper.

        Parameters:
        parameterName - The name of the parameter to return the associated value of.
        Returns:
        The value associated with the provided parameterName. Returns null if the FormDataMapper isContained no mapping for the provided parameterName.

      • has

        boolean has(java.lang.String parameterName)
        Returns true if the ParameterDataMapper isContained the provided a value for the provided parameterName.

        The method must not return true if the value associated with the provided parameterName equals null.

        Parameters:
        parameterName - The parameterName to check for in the ParameterDataMapper.
        Returns:
        true if the ParameterDataMapper isContained the provided a value for the provided parameterName.
